<% @current_tab = :Home %>
<% content_for :head do %>
	<%= stylesheet_link_tag('home') %>
	<%= javascript_include_tag('home') %>
<% end %>
<div id="main_content" class="login">
	<div class="content_bar" id="top">
		<div class="content">
			<h4>Welcome to the TGFE Network</h4>
			<p>Take a moment to look around, and when you&rsquo;re ready, come take a course, check out the new articles, respond to a discussion, or meet fellow site members.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<ul class="section_list">
		<li class="library">
			<h4><span>Browse Library</span></h4>
			<p>Filled with content by visionaries who share your interest in sacred evolution, the library is a rich resource for learning more about the Great Story. <%= link_to "Go to Library", signup_url, :class => "more" %><span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></p>
		</li>
		<li class="courses">
			<h4><span>Take Courses</span></h4>
			<p>Take free multimedia courses that expand upon the material in TGFE (and serve as an excellent introduction if you've yet to read the book). <%= link_to "Go to Courses", signup_url, :class => "more" %><span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></p>
		</li>
		<li class="discussions">
			<h4><span>Join Discussions</span></h4>
			<p>Discuss what you're learning, discovering, and wondering with leaders and peers alike. Our discussion area is there for the community to explore new ideas, ask important questions, and exchange stories. <%= link_to "Go to Discussions", signup_url, :class => "more" %><span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></p>
		</li>
		<li class="people">
			<h4><span>Meet People</span></h4>
			<p>Connect with other inspired (and inspiring) individuals from around the world who also want to create a better future. Post your own profile, with your bio and interests, and contact other members directly from the website. <%= link_to "Go to People", signup_url, :class => "more" %><span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></p>
		</li>
	</ul>
</div>
<div id="sidebar">
	<ul class="modules">
		<li class="cta register">
			<div class="content">
				<h4 class="get_premium replace">Get Premium Access</h4>
				<p>ThankGodForEvolution.net is provided free of charge, and depends on the generosity of its members. <a class="more" href="http://www.thankgodforevolution.com/donate">Make a donation today</a><span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></p>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ul>
</div>